performance monitoring packages.",
        benefits: [
          "Professional Credibility",
          "Lead Generation",
          "SEO-Optimized",
          "Mobile-Responsive",
        ],
      },
      {
        name: "Corporate Website",
        description:
          "Corporate websites demand authority, professionalism, and a seamless user experience that reflects the scale of your enterprise. EDMA, based in Indore and serving Fortune-class businesses across India and globally, designs corporate websites that command respect from the first second a visitor lands. Our corporate web design process is trusted by companies across Madhya Pradesh, India's major metros, and international markets.\n\nWhy Corporate Website Design Matters: Your corporate website is often the first point of contact for investors, partners, clients, and prospective employees worldwide. A sophisticated digital presence signals stability, capability, and professionalism. In today's B2B landscape, 94% of first impressions are design-related — and a subpar corporate website can cost you enterprise deals worth millions. Corporate websites that achieve top-3 Google rankings for industry keywords generate 5–10x more qualified B2B leads.\n\nOur Approach at EDMA (Indore & Global): Our corporate web design process begins with in-depth brand discovery — understanding your company's values, stakeholders, and competitive positioning — then translating that into a sophisticated digital platform. We build multi-department site architectures, investor relations portals, leadership pages, career sections, and comprehensive about pages. Every corporate website is W3C compliant, WCAG accessible, and optimized with structured data markup.\n\nKey Benefits: Enterprise Authority design that commands immediate respect; Stakeholder Trust through transparent, well-structured content; Global Brand Reach with multilingual and international SEO support; Accessibility Compliant to WCAG 2.1 AA standards. Performance scores consistently above 90 on Google PageSpeed across Indore, India, and global deployments.\n\nFAQ: Can EDMA handle large corporate websites with hundreds of pages? Absolutely — we specialize in scalable enterprise architectures. Do you support corporate intranets? Yes, we design and develop internal portals alongside public-facing corporate websites.",
