      {
        name: "E-Commerce Website",
        description:
          "E-commerce is a multi-trillion dollar global industry, and your online store needs to be built for maximum conversions. EDMA's e-commerce website designing team in Indore creates stunning, high-performance online stores for businesses across India and worldwide. From local Indore retailers going digital to global D2C brands, we engineer e-commerce experiences that turn browsers into buyers and buyers into loyal customers.\n\nWhy E-Commerce Website Design Matters: A poorly optimized e-commerce website loses 68% of potential customers to cart abandonment. Slow load times cost Indian e-commerce businesses alone billions of rupees annually in lost revenue. Conversely, professional e-commerce design with strategic product presentation, trust signals, and optimized checkout flows can increase conversion rates by 200–400%. Global e-commerce crossed $6 trillion in 2023 — the opportunity is enormous for businesses with the right digital storefront.\n\nOur Approach at EDMA (Indore & Global): We design product pages that sell, category pages optimized for search, and checkout flows that reduce abandonment to single digits. Our e-commerce designs integrate seamlessly with payment gateways including Razorpay, PayPal, Stripe, and international processors — supporting INR and multi-currency transactions. Every product listing is structured with rich schema markup for Google Shopping eligibility. Trust signals — SSL badges, reviews, secure payment icons — are strategically embedded throughout the buyer journey.\n\nKey Benefits: Higher Conversion Rate through CRO-optimized layouts; Multi-Currency Support for Indian and global sales; Secure Payment Integration with all major gateways; Google Shopping Ready with product schema markup. Perfect for Indore businesses, India-wide brands, and international e-commerce operations.\n\nFAQ: Can you migrate my existing store to a new platform? Yes — EDMA handles full e-commerce migrations with zero product data loss. Do you design for Shopify and WooCommerce? Absolutely — we work across all major platforms and custom solutions.",
