      {
        name: "Portfolio Website",
        description:
          "Your portfolio website is your most powerful sales tool — a curated showcase of your best work that speaks louder than any pitch. EDMA designs stunning portfolio websites for freelancers, creative professionals, agencies, and studios across Indore, India, and international markets. In a globally competitive creative economy, your portfolio website is the difference between winning premium clients and being overlooked.\n\nWhy Portfolio Website Design Matters: Creative professionals with professionally designed portfolio websites command fees 40–60% higher than those relying on social media profiles alone. Potential clients make hiring decisions within 3–7 seconds of landing on your portfolio — which means your first impression must be extraordinary. A well-structured, fast-loading portfolio website with strategic SEO also ranks for your specialty keywords, bringing clients to you passively without expensive advertising.\n\nOur Approach at EDMA (Indore & Global): We craft visually striking layouts with immersive project showcases, smooth scroll animations, and galleries that make your work impossible to ignore. Each portfolio site includes an SEO-optimized about page, service offerings section, client testimonials, case study deep-dives, and a frictionless contact system. We optimize for Core Web Vitals ensuring sub-2-second load times that keep impatient clients engaged.\n\nKey Benefits: Stunning Visual Showcase with immersive project galleries; Fast and Immersive with sub-2-second load performance; Client-Winning Design that positions you as a premium professional; SEO for Freelancers targeting specialty and location keywords. Serving photographers, architects, UI/UX designers, filmmakers, illustrators, and agencies across Indore, India, and globally.\n\nFAQ: How many portfolio projects should I feature? We recommend 8–15 of your strongest, most relevant projects for maximum impact. Can I update my portfolio myself after launch? Yes — we build on CMS platforms so you can add and update projects without developer assistance.",
