across Indore, across India, and internationally.\n\nFAQ: Can you integrate our website with our existing student management software? Yes — EDMA integrates with all major student information systems and LMS platforms. Do you offer multilingual support for regional language content? Absolutely — we build educational websites in Hindi, English, and other regional Indian languages.",
