ia.\n\nFAQ: Can EDMA build a custom LMS from scratch? Yes — we build fully custom LMS platforms with proprietary features when off-the-shelf solutions don't meet your needs. How long does it take to build an LMS website? Depending on features required, typical LMS website projects take 4–8 weeks from discovery to launch.",
