      {
        name: "E-commerce Development",
        description:
          "E-commerce Development is one of the highest-ROI digital investments a business can make. EDMA — a leading e-commerce development company in Indore, India — builds high-converting online stores that generate real revenue, not just traffic. We specialize in custom e-commerce platforms, WooCommerce, Shopify, Magento, and headless commerce architectures for clients across India and worldwide.\n\nWhat We Build: Our e-commerce solutions include full product catalog management with variant support, multi-currency and multi-language capabilities, abandoned cart recovery flows, loyalty programs, subscription billing, B2B bulk ordering portals, and advanced analytics dashboards showing your sales performance in real time.\n\nConversion Optimization by Design: Every decision is guided by CRO principles. We implement one-click checkout, guest purchase flows, trust badges, product review systems, and urgency triggers that collectively increase average order value and reduce cart abandonment.\n\nPayment & Logistics Integration: We integrate Razorpay, Stripe, PayPal, PayU, UPI, and BNPL options. Shipping integrations include Shiprocket, Delhivery, FedEx, and automated tax calculation for GST compliance in India and VAT compliance globally.\n\nPerformance & SEO: Our e-commerce stores load in under 2 seconds, with structured data markup for Google Shopping, SEO-optimized category and product pages, and image compression pipelines. Trusted by businesses in Indore, Madhya Pradesh, across India, and international markets.\n\nFAQ: How long does it take to launch an e-commerce store? A standard store with 50–500 products takes 6–12 weeks. Complex multi-vendor marketplaces may take 3–6 months.",
        benefits: [
