      {
        name: "CMS Development",
        description:
          "CMS (Content Management System) Development empowers your business to publish, manage, and update website content without writing a single line of code. EDMA is a specialized CMS development company in Indore, India, building custom and platform-based CMS solutions for businesses of all sizes — from local Indore enterprises to multinational corporations in the USA, UK, and Australia.\n\nPlatforms We Work With: WordPress, Drupal, Joomla, Contentful, Strapi, Sanity, Directus, and fully custom-built CMS platforms tailored to your content workflow. We choose the right platform based on your team's technical comfort level, content volume, and integration requirements.\n\nCustom CMS vs Off-the-Shelf: Off-the-shelf CMS platforms work well for standard websites, but growing businesses often need custom workflows, approval pipelines, multi-site management, and content localization features that generic platforms cannot provide. Our custom CMS solutions are built precisely around your editorial process.\n\nKey Features We Build: Drag-and-drop page builders, WYSIWYG editors, scheduled content publishing, SEO metadata management per page, media asset libraries with CDN delivery, role-based editorial access (editor, reviewer, publisher), multi-language content management, and REST/GraphQL API exposure for headless delivery.\n\nSEO Benefits: Proper CMS architecture means every page has editable meta titles, descriptions, canonical URLs, structured data, and sitemap generation — critical for Google rankings. Serving Indore, Jabalpur, Raipur, and global content-heavy businesses with CMS training and ongoing support.\n\nFAQ: Can I manage my CMS without technical knowledge? Absolutely. We provide training sessions and documentation so your team can confidently manage all content independently from day one.",
