      {
        name: "Custom Web Development",
        description:
          "Custom Web Development is the gold standard for businesses that need a solution built specifically around their unique processes, brand identity, and growth ambitions. EDMA is a premier custom web development firm based in Indore, India, delivering bespoke web solutions to clients across healthcare, finance, education, manufacturing, logistics, and retail sectors globally.\n\nWhy Custom Over Templates: Template-based websites hit ceilings quickly — they cannot handle complex business logic, unique user flows, advanced integrations, or the performance requirements of high-traffic applications. Custom development eliminates all limitations and gives you a competitive technological moat.\n\nOur Custom Development Process: Discovery and Requirements Analysis, System Architecture Design, UI/UX Wireframing, Iterative Development Sprints, QA Testing, Staged Deployment, and Post-Launch Support. We follow Agile methodology with 2-week sprint cycles, giving you complete visibility and control throughout the build.\n\nTechnologies Used: React/Next.js (front end), Node.js/Django/Laravel (back end), PostgreSQL/MongoDB (databases), Redis (caching), AWS/GCP (cloud infrastructure), Docker/Kubernetes (containerization), and automated testing with Jest and Cypress.\n\nIP Ownership and Security: You own 100% of the source code. No licensing dependencies, no vendor lock-in, and no recurring platform fees beyond hosting. Our code is documented, version-controlled, and auditable. Proud to serve businesses in Indore, across Madhya Pradesh, pan-India, and internationally.\n\nFAQ: How much does custom web development cost? A custom business application typically ranges from Rs 2–10 lakh for mid-complexity projects. We provide a detailed quote after the discovery call.",
