      {
        name: "Web Application Development",
        description:
          "Web Application Development transforms your business idea into a powerful, interactive digital tool accessible from any browser on any device — no installation required. EDMA builds enterprise-grade web applications in Indore, India, for clients across industries including SaaS platforms, workflow automation tools, real-time collaboration apps, ERP systems, and customer-facing portals.\n\nWhat Sets Web Apps Apart: Unlike static websites, web applications handle complex user interactions, real-time data processing, multi-user collaboration, and deep integrations with external systems. Think Google Docs, Trello, or project management tools — EDMA builds solutions at that level of sophistication for your specific domain.\n\nCore Technologies: React/Next.js or Angular for the front end; Node.js, Python, or Go for the back end; WebSockets for real-time features; PostgreSQL or MongoDB for data persistence; Redis for session management and caching; AWS Lambda for serverless operations.\n\nFeatures We Regularly Build: Multi-tenant architecture for SaaS products; real-time dashboards with live data updates; complex form systems with conditional logic; PDF/Excel report generation; in-app notification systems; advanced search and filtering; bulk data import/export; subscription and billing management.\n\nGlobal Delivery, Indore Roots: Our development team is based in Indore, MP, with project management processes serving clients across the USA, Canada, UK, Europe, and Southeast Asia with timezone-aligned communication.\n\nFAQ: What is the difference between a website and a web application? A website primarily delivers information. A web application enables users to perform complex tasks, manage data, and interact dynamically — like an app, but in a browser.",
