      {
        name: "Mobile-Responsive Development",
        description:
          "Mobile-Responsive Development ensures your website delivers a flawless experience across every screen size — from 320px smartphones to 4K ultrawide monitors. With 60% of global web traffic now coming from mobile devices, responsive development is not optional — it is the baseline for SEO rankings, user retention, and conversion rates. EDMA's responsive development team in Indore, India, builds and retrofits websites for perfect mobile performance.\n\nGoogle Mobile-First Indexing: Since 2021, Google uses the mobile version of your website as the primary signal for search rankings. A non-responsive site is actively penalized in search results. Our responsive development ensures your site passes Google Mobile-Friendly Test with flying colors.\n\nOur Responsive Development Stack: We use CSS Grid and Flexbox for fluid layouts, Tailwind CSS for utility-first responsive design, and custom media queries for precise breakpoint control. All components are built mobile-first, then progressively enhanced for larger screens.\n\nPerformance on Mobile: We implement image optimization (WebP/AVIF formats), lazy loading, preconnect hints, and Service Workers to achieve fast load times even on 3G connections.\n\nTesting Process: We test on 20+ device configurations including iPhone, Samsung Galaxy, OnePlus, and tablets, using both physical devices and BrowserStack for comprehensive coverage. Serving businesses across Indore, MP, India, and globally who want to stop losing mobile visitors.\n\nFAQ: My existing site is not mobile-friendly — can you fix it? Yes. We offer responsive retrofitting services that update your existing site without rebuilding from scratch, saving 40–60% of full redevelopment costs.",
