        name: "UI/UX Development",
        description:
          "UI/UX Development is where visual design meets functional engineering — transforming wireframes and design files into pixel-perfect, interaction-rich, accessible web experiences. EDMA is a specialized UI/UX development studio in Indore, India, translating Figma, Adobe XD, and Sketch designs into production-ready React, Vue, or Angular components for clients worldwide.\n\nThe Value of Expert UI/UX Implementation: Even the most brilliant design fails when implemented poorly. Poor animation performance, misaligned spacing, inconsistent interaction states, and accessibility violations destroy the user experience your designers worked hard to create. Our implementation specialists ensure design fidelity is maintained at 100%.\n\nWhat We Implement: Design system component libraries with Storybook documentation; micro-interactions and animations using Framer Motion and GSAP; skeleton loading states; complex form validation UX; onboarding tour flows; tooltip systems; modal and sheet architectures; responsive navigation patterns; dark/light mode systems.\n\nAccessibility Standards: We implement ARIA labels, focus management, keyboard navigation, and screen reader compatibility as standard. WCAG 2.1 AA compliance is our baseline, with AAA compliance available for government and enterprise clients.\n\nPerformance of UI Components: Our components are optimized with React.memo, useMemo, and code splitting to ensure UI rendering never blocks the main thread. Serving design agencies, product companies, and startups in Indore, across India, and globally seeking flawless design-to-code translation.\n\nFAQ: Can you implement designs created by our in-house designer? Absolutely. We work from Figma, Adobe XD, Sketch, InVision, Zeplin, or even PDF mockups and deliver pixel-accurate implementation.",
