        description:
          "API Development and Integration is the connective tissue of the modern web — enabling your website, app, and third-party tools to communicate, share data, and work as one unified system. EDMA is an expert API development and integration company in Indore, India, building robust RESTful APIs, GraphQL APIs, and WebSocket endpoints, plus integrating hundreds of third-party services for clients globally.\n\nWhat We Build: Custom REST and GraphQL APIs with OpenAPI/Swagger documentation; OAuth2 and JWT authentication systems; webhook receivers and dispatchers; rate-limited public APIs for your product; API versioning and deprecation management; real-time APIs using WebSockets and Server-Sent Events.\n\nThird-Party Integrations We Specialize In: Payment gateways (Razorpay, Stripe, PayPal); CRM systems (Salesforce, HubSpot, Zoho); ERP integrations (SAP, Oracle, Tally); Email platforms (SendGrid, Mailchimp, AWS SES); SMS/WhatsApp (Twilio, MSG91); Shipping (Shiprocket, FedEx, DHL); Social media APIs; Google Maps and location services; Analytics platforms.\n\nAPI Security: All APIs we build include input validation, SQL injection prevention, XSS protection, CORS configuration, API key management, IP whitelisting options, and request logging for audit trails.\n\nDocumentation and Testing: We provide complete Postman collections and OpenAPI specs with every API project, along with automated integration tests that verify API contracts are never broken during deployments. Serving tech companies and SaaS platforms in Indore and globally.\n\nFAQ: How long does API development take? A standard CRUD API takes 2–4 weeks. Complex multi-system integrations may take 6–12 weeks depending on third-party API availability.",
