      {
        name: "Static Website Development",
        description:
          "Static Website Development produces the fastest, most secure, and most cost-effective websites on the internet — pre-built HTML, CSS, and JavaScript files served directly from a CDN with zero server processing. EDMA's Jamstack and static site specialists in Indore, India, build lightning-fast static sites using Next.js, Gatsby, Astro, Hugo, and Eleventy for clients worldwide.\n\nWhy Static Sites Win on Performance: A static site served from a CDN edge node near your visitor delivers the first byte in under 50ms — 10–20x faster than a traditionally server-rendered page. This directly boosts Core Web Vitals scores, Google search rankings, and conversion rates.\n\nWhen Static Is the Right Choice: Marketing websites, landing pages, documentation sites, portfolio sites, company brochure sites, blogs, and event microsites are all perfect candidates for static development.\n\nModern Static with Dynamic Capabilities: Static does not mean limited. We use incremental static regeneration (ISR) with Next.js to rebuild only changed pages, headless CMS integration (Contentful, Sanity, Strapi) for content management, and serverless functions for dynamic features like contact forms, search, and user authentication.\n\nHosting and Cost: Static sites can be hosted on Vercel, Netlify, Cloudflare Pages, or AWS S3+CloudFront for very low monthly costs — far cheaper than managed server hosting, with better uptime (99.99%) and automatic global scaling. Serving businesses across Indore, MP, and globally.\n\nFAQ: Can a static site be updated without a developer? Yes. With a headless CMS integration, your team can publish content changes through a friendly dashboard, and the site auto-rebuilds and deploys in 2–5 minutes.",
