        description:
          "Website Maintenance and Support is the ongoing care that keeps your digital asset secure, fast, up-to-date, and revenue-generating every single day. A neglected website loses rankings, accumulates security vulnerabilities, suffers from broken functionality, and ultimately costs far more in emergency repairs than regular maintenance would have. EDMA offers comprehensive website maintenance plans from Indore, India, for businesses globally.\n\nWhat Our Maintenance Plans Cover: Regular CMS, plugin, and dependency updates; security monitoring with malware scanning and automated patching; uptime monitoring with instant SMS/email alerts; weekly automated backups to off-site storage; performance monitoring with Core Web Vitals tracking; monthly SEO health checks; bug fixes for existing functionality; content updates (text, images, products); SSL certificate management and renewal.\n\nWhy Regular Maintenance Matters: 39% of website breaches occur through outdated plugins or themes. Google penalizes slow sites and rewards fast ones — regular performance maintenance directly impacts your search rankings. Browser updates can break JavaScript compatibility, and regular testing catches these issues before they impact customers.\n\nMaintenance Plan Tiers: Basic Plan (security, backups, uptime monitoring); Standard Plan (adds performance optimization and 5 content updates/month); Premium Plan (adds priority support, dedicated developer hours, and monthly strategy calls).\n\nEmergency Support: We offer 4-hour SLA emergency response for critical production issues on premium plans. Serving businesses in Indore, across India, and internationally who want peace of mind and a proactive digital partner.\n\nFAQ: What if I already have a developer but want maintenance only? We offer maintenance-only contracts with no long-term commitment, starting from Rs 3,000/month for basic security and uptime coverage.",
