      {
        name: "Website Migration Services",
        description:
          "Website Migration Services transfer your website from one platform, hosting provider, or technology stack to another — safely, without data loss, SEO ranking drops, or downtime. EDMA is an experienced website migration specialist based in Indore, India, handling platform migrations, CMS upgrades, server migrations, and domain transitions for businesses across India and globally.\n\nTypes of Migrations We Handle: WordPress to headless CMS; Magento to Shopify or WooCommerce; shared hosting to cloud (AWS/GCP/Azure); HTTP to HTTPS with full SSL; domain migrations with 301 redirect mapping; database migrations across MySQL, PostgreSQL, and MongoDB; legacy PHP applications to modern Node.js or Laravel; static HTML sites to WordPress or Webflow.\n\nSEO Preservation Protocol: Migration is one of the highest-risk events for SEO rankings. We create comprehensive URL mapping with 301 redirects for every changed URL, migrate all meta tags and structured data, submit updated sitemaps to Google Search Console, and monitor ranking changes post-migration with immediate corrective action if drops occur.\n\nZero-Downtime Migration: For business-critical websites, we execute migrations using a parallel run strategy — the new system runs alongside the old, with a DNS switch-over that takes milliseconds. Your visitors experience zero downtime, and rollback is instant if needed.\n\nData Migration Quality Assurance: We validate every record, attachment, relationship, and user account after migration with automated reconciliation testing. Serving businesses across Indore, India, and internationally who are outgrowing their current platform.\n\nFAQ: Will I lose my Google rankings during migration? Not if done correctly. Our SEO preservation protocol maintains 95%+ of rankings through migrations, with full recovery typically within 4–6 weeks.",
