      {
        name: "Security & SSL Implementation",
        description:
          "Website Security and SSL Implementation protects your business, your customers, and your reputation from the ever-growing threat of cyberattacks, data breaches, and compliance violations. EDMA provides comprehensive web security services from Indore, India, implementing defense-in-depth security architectures for e-commerce sites, web applications, SaaS platforms, and corporate websites globally.\n\nSSL/TLS Certificate Implementation: We install and configure SSL certificates (Let Encrypt, Comodo, DigiCert, Wildcard certificates) with HSTS headers, HTTPS redirect enforcement, and proper certificate chain configuration. An active SSL certificate is required for Google rankings, payment processing, and customer trust.\n\nSecurity Hardening We Implement: Web Application Firewall (WAF) configuration with Cloudflare or AWS WAF; DDoS protection; SQL injection and XSS prevention through input validation and Content Security Policy headers; brute force protection with login rate limiting; two-factor authentication systems; automated vulnerability scanning with weekly reports; secrets management with environment variable auditing.\n\nCompliance Implementation: PCI-DSS compliance for payment-handling websites; GDPR compliance with cookie consent management, data retention policies, and privacy-by-design implementation; HIPAA security controls for healthcare applications; ISO 27001 security framework alignment.\n\nSecurity Monitoring: Real-time intrusion detection, malware scanning, file integrity monitoring, and 24/7 alerting with documented incident response procedures. Our security operations team responds to critical alerts within 1 hour. Serving e-commerce, healthcare, finance, and government-adjacent businesses across Indore, India, and globally.\n\nFAQ: My website was hacked — can you help? Yes. We offer emergency malware removal and security hardening services with a typical 24–48 hour remediation timeline for compromised sites.",
