        name: "AI & Chatbot Integration",
        description:
          "AI and Chatbot Integration brings the power of artificial intelligence directly into your website — automating customer support, qualifying leads 24/7, personalizing user experiences, and driving measurable business outcomes without increasing headcount. EDMA is a forward-thinking AI integration agency based in Indore, India, implementing intelligent chatbots and AI-powered features for businesses across India and globally in e-commerce, healthcare, education, finance, and SaaS sectors.\n\nWhat We Build: Custom AI chatbots trained on your product knowledge base and FAQs; lead qualification bots that collect contact details and schedule meetings automatically; support deflection bots that resolve 60–80% of common queries without human intervention; AI-powered search with natural language queries; product recommendation engines; sentiment analysis for customer feedback; AI content generators for product descriptions and email personalization.\n\nPlatforms and Technologies We Work With: OpenAI GPT-4/4o API for conversational AI and content generation; Anthropic Claude for nuanced, context-aware conversations; Google Dialogflow for enterprise-grade NLP; Botpress for open-source chatbot development; Intercom and Freshchat for customer support automation; LangChain for building multi-step AI agents; vector databases (Pinecone, Weaviate) for semantic search and RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation).\n\nROI of AI Integration: Businesses implementing AI chatbots report 67% reduction in support ticket volume, 3x increase in lead capture rate outside business hours, and 40% improvement in first-response time satisfaction scores. The average payback period for AI chatbot investment is under 6 months.\n\nIntegration Targets: Website chat widgets; WhatsApp Business; Facebook Messenger; Slack; Microsoft Teams; CRM systems (HubSpot, Salesforce); helpdesk platforms (Zendesk, Freshdesk). Serving innovative businesses in Indore, across India, and globally.\n\nFAQ: Can the AI chatbot learn from our specific business data? Yes. We implement RAG pipelines that ground the AI in your specific documentation, products, policies, and FAQs — eliminating hallucinations and ensuring accurate, brand-consistent responses.",
