      {
        name: "API Integration Services",
        description:
          "Modern mobile apps derive much of their value from integrations — connecting to payment systems, mapping services, social platforms, communication tools, analytics engines, and industry-specific data providers. EDMA, a specialist in API integration services for mobile apps in Indore, handles the full complexity of integrating third-party APIs into your application so your team can focus on building your core product. Our API integration team has experience with hundreds of APIs across every major category: payment gateways (Razorpay, Stripe, PayPal, UPI, Paytm), mapping and location services (Google Maps, Mapbox, HERE), communication (Twilio, SendGrid, WhatsApp Business API), social login (Google, Facebook, Apple, LinkedIn), cloud services (AWS, Firebase, Azure), AI and ML services (OpenAI, Google AI, AWS AI services), and industry-specific APIs in healthcare, logistics, finance, and e-commerce. We don't just connect APIs — we architect integrations properly, with secure credential management, error handling, retry logic, rate limit management, and monitoring. EDMA builds API abstraction layers that make your codebase maintainable and allow you to swap or upgrade third-party services without rebuilding your app. We also develop custom REST and GraphQL APIs, webhook implementations, and real-time data pipelines for businesses with unique data integration needs. Our API work covers both mobile and backend integration, ensuring your app communicates efficiently with all external systems. Businesses across India and globally trust EDMA to handle their most complex integration challenges — from fintech payment rails to healthcare data exchanges. Supercharge your mobile app with the right integrations — talk to EDMA's API specialists today.",
