          "Getting your app live on the App Store and Google Play is more complex than most businesses realize — and how you do it dramatically impacts your app's long-term visibility and download volume. EDMA provides expert App Store Deployment & Optimization services from Indore, helping businesses across India and globally launch successfully and rank higher in search results. Our App Store Optimization (ASO) specialists treat the App Store and Google Play as search engines — because that's exactly what they are. Over 65% of app downloads come from store search, making ASO a critical component of mobile growth strategy. EDMA's ASO service covers keyword research and strategy, title and subtitle optimization, description writing with high-volume keywords, screenshot design and A/B testing, preview video production, category selection, and ongoing ranking monitoring and iteration. We analyze competitor apps, identify ranking opportunities, and craft store listings that convert browsers into downloaders. Beyond optimization, our deployment service handles the technical side of App Store submission — provisioning profiles, signing certificates, build configuration, TestFlight beta testing, App Store review navigation, and Google Play Console management. We have a proven track record of getting apps approved quickly, including apps in complex categories like healthcare, fintech, and social networking that have stricter review requirements. Post-launch, EDMA monitors your rankings, reviews, and conversion rates, making continuous optimizations to ensure sustained growth. With EDMA managing your App Store presence, you can focus on building a great product while we maximize your organic discovery and download velocity. Contact us for an ASO audit of your existing app.",
