      {
        name: "App Security Services",
        description:
          "Mobile app security is not optional — a single breach can destroy user trust, result in regulatory penalties, and cause irreparable brand damage. EDMA, a specialist mobile app security company in Indore, provides comprehensive security assessment and implementation services to protect your app, your users, and your business from the ever-evolving landscape of mobile threats. Our security team conducts thorough penetration testing of your mobile app and its backend, identifying vulnerabilities including insecure data storage, weak authentication, unencrypted network traffic, improper session management, code injection vulnerabilities, reverse engineering risks, and insecure API endpoints. We follow the OWASP Mobile Security Testing Guide (MSTG) and OWASP Top 10 Mobile Risks framework to ensure systematic, comprehensive coverage. EDMA's security implementation services include end-to-end encryption for sensitive data, certificate pinning to prevent man-in-the-middle attacks, root/jailbreak detection, obfuscation and binary protection to prevent reverse engineering, biometric authentication integration, secure key storage using Android Keystore and iOS Secure Enclave, and runtime application self-protection (RASP). We provide detailed security assessment reports with prioritized findings and remediation guidance, and our team can implement the fixes directly. For businesses in regulated industries — healthcare, fintech, legal, and government — EDMA ensures your app meets HIPAA, GDPR, PCI DSS, and local Indian data protection regulation requirements. We also provide ongoing security monitoring and periodic re-testing as your app evolves. Protect your users, protect your business — partner with EDMA for enterprise-grade mobile app security. Get a free initial security consultation today.",
