      {
        name: "Logo Design",
        description:
          "Your logo is the cornerstone of your brand identity — the first visual impression every customer has of your business. At EDMA, a top-rated logo design agency in Indore, India, we craft timeless, versatile logos that work across every medium — from business cards and websites to billboards and packaging — capturing your brand essence in a single, unforgettable mark.\n\nOur Logo Design Process: We begin with an in-depth brand discovery session to understand your values, target audience, competitors, and market positioning. Our designers then explore multiple creative directions, presenting 3–5 unique logo concepts for your review. Each concept is refined through collaborative feedback until you have a logo you're proud to put on everything.\n\nTypes of Logos We Create: Wordmarks (text-only logos), lettermarks (monogram logos), pictorial marks (icon-based logos), abstract marks, combination marks, and emblem logos. We design for scalability — every logo looks sharp at 16×16 pixels on a favicon and stunning at 40 feet on a billboard.\n\nWhat You Receive: Full-resolution vector files (AI, EPS, SVG), raster exports (PNG transparent, JPG), color variations (full color, monochrome, reversed), brand color codes (HEX, RGB, CMYK, Pantone), typography specifications, and a brand usage guidelines document. Serving businesses in Indore, Bhopal, Mumbai, Delhi, Bangalore, and internationally across the USA, UK, UAE, and Australia.\n\nFAQ: How long does logo design take? Standard logo projects are delivered in 5–10 business days with 2 rounds of revisions included. Rush delivery is available.",
