        name: "Banner & Ad Design",
        description:
          "High-converting banners and ads are the engine of successful digital marketing campaigns. EDMA's banner and ad design service in Indore, India, creates visually compelling, click-worthy creative assets for Google Display Ads, Facebook/Instagram Ads, LinkedIn Ads, programmatic display, and website banners that drive measurable ROI for clients worldwide.\n\nTypes of Ads We Design: Google Display Network banners (all 12 standard sizes including leaderboard, rectangle, half-page, and mobile banner), Facebook and Instagram ad creatives (static, carousel, and story formats), LinkedIn sponsored content graphics, YouTube video thumbnails and pre-roll frames, retargeting banner sets, A/B test creative variations, and seasonal promotional banners.\n\nConversion-Focused Design Principles: Every banner is designed with a clear visual hierarchy — attention-grabbing headline, compelling visual, concise value proposition, and a high-contrast CTA button that drives clicks. We apply color psychology and whitespace principles to maximize message clarity at a glance.\n\nA/B Testing Support: We design 2–3 creative variations per ad set to enable split testing, providing data-driven insights on which visuals, messaging, and CTAs perform best with your target audience.\n\nTurnaround and Formats: Standard banner sets delivered in 3–5 business days. All files delivered in PNG, JPG, GIF, and HTML5 animated formats as required by your ad platform. Serving Indore, India-wide, and international advertising campaigns.\n\nFAQ: What sizes do I need for Google Display Ads? We recommend the 12 most effective sizes covering 90% of ad inventory — we design the complete set for maximum reach.",
