          "A great poster communicates a powerful message in seconds — capturing attention, conveying information, and inspiring action before the viewer moves on. EDMA's poster design service in Indore, India, creates striking posters for events, promotions, product launches, social causes, education, corporate communications, and cultural campaigns for clients across India and globally.\n\nTypes of Posters We Design: Event posters (concerts, conferences, exhibitions, sports events), promotional posters (sales, product launches, offers), educational posters (awareness campaigns, infographic posters), corporate announcement posters, motivational and office wall art, film and entertainment posters, election campaign posters, and digital posters optimized for social sharing.\n\nDesign Principles We Apply: Visual hierarchy that guides the eye from headline to key information to CTA; strong typographic contrast for readability at distance; color harmony that evokes the right emotional response; and compositional balance that makes the design feel intentional and professional.\n\nPrint vs Digital Optimization: For print posters, we work in CMYK color mode with 300 DPI resolution and bleed margins, ensuring perfect output on any professional printer. For digital posters, we deliver RGB files optimized for screen display and social sharing.\n\nFile Delivery: High-resolution print-ready PDF (with bleeds and crop marks), PNG/JPG for digital use, and editable source files on request. Serving businesses, NGOs, event organizers, and institutions across Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India, and internationally.\n\nFAQ: Can you design a poster if I only have a rough idea? Yes — our creative brief process helps us capture your vision even if you cannot articulate it precisely. We turn rough ideas into stunning visuals.",
