      {
        name: "Search Engine Optimization (SEO)",
        description:
          "Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is the most powerful long-term digital marketing strategy for sustainable business growth. At Elite Digital Marketing Agency (EDMA) in Indore, India, we provide comprehensive SEO services that help businesses rank on the first page of Google for high-intent keywords — driving qualified organic traffic that converts into leads and revenue.\n\nWhat We Do: Our SEO process covers technical SEO audits, on-page optimization, content strategy, link building, schema markup, and local SEO — all aligned to Google's latest algorithms including Core Web Vitals, E-E-A-T guidelines, and helpful content updates. We analyze 200+ ranking factors to build a tailored SEO roadmap for your business.\n\nTechnical SEO Excellence: We fix crawl errors, optimize site architecture, implement structured data, improve page speed, and ensure mobile-first indexing compliance. Our technical foundation ensures search engines can discover, index, and rank every page of your website effectively.\n\nContent & Link Strategy: Our SEO content team creates topical authority clusters — in-depth, semantically rich content that satisfies both users and search engines. Our link building campaigns secure placements on high-DA, niche-relevant websites to build your domain's authority organically.\n\nLocal & Global SEO: We specialize in local SEO for businesses in Indore, Madhya Pradesh, and across India, helping you dominate local search results. For global clients, we execute international SEO strategies targeting the USA, UK, Australia, Canada, and UAE markets.\n\nFAQ: How long does SEO take to show results? Typically 3–6 months for competitive keywords; local and long-tail keywords can rank in 4–8 weeks. Is SEO better than paid ads? SEO provides compounding, sustainable traffic at zero ongoing cost per click — making it the highest long-term ROI channel for most businesses.",
