        description:
          "Email Marketing delivers the highest ROI of any digital marketing channel — averaging ₹3,600 return for every ₹100 invested. EDMA's email marketing specialists design, build, and automate email campaigns that nurture leads, retain customers, and drive repeat revenue for businesses across India and globally.\n\nOur Email Marketing Services: Campaign strategy and planning, responsive HTML email design, list building and segmentation, automated drip sequences, welcome series, abandoned cart recovery, re-engagement campaigns, newsletter management, A/B testing, and deliverability optimization.\n\nAdvanced Segmentation & Personalization: Generic blast emails are dead. We segment your email list by behavior, demographics, purchase history, and engagement level — delivering hyper-personalized messages that speak directly to each subscriber's needs and position in the buying cycle. Personalized emails generate 6x higher transaction rates.\n\nMarketing Automation: We build automated email workflows that trigger based on user actions — website visits, form submissions, purchases, or inactivity. Your email marketing works around the clock, nurturing leads and recovering lost sales without manual effort.\n\nDeliverability Excellence: We maintain sender reputation, authenticate domains (SPF, DKIM, DMARC), manage list hygiene, and monitor inbox placement rates to ensure your emails reach the inbox — not the spam folder.\n\nMeasurable Results: Every campaign is tracked with open rates, click rates, conversion rates, and revenue attribution. Our clients consistently achieve open rates 2x the industry average. Serving businesses in Indore, across India, and internationally including the USA, UK, Australia, and UAE.\n\nFAQ: What email platform do you use? We work with Mailchimp, Klaviyo, ConvertKit, HubSpot, and others based on your needs. How often should I send marketing emails? For most businesses, 1–2 emails per week is optimal to maintain engagement without causing un