      {
        name: "Online Reputation Management (ORM)",
        description:
          "Online Reputation Management (ORM) is essential in today's digital landscape where a single negative review or news article can damage years of brand building. EDMA provides comprehensive ORM services to businesses across India and globally — monitoring, managing, and improving your online reputation to protect revenue and restore trust.\n\nWhat ORM Covers: 24/7 brand mention monitoring, negative content suppression, proactive review generation, review response management across Google, Justdial, MagicBricks, Clutch, Glassdoor, and social platforms, Wikipedia management, search results management, crisis response, and reputation recovery campaigns.\n\nBrand Monitoring: We use enterprise-grade monitoring tools to track every mention of your brand across search engines, social media, news sites, forums, and review platforms in real time. Instant alerts allow rapid response to negative content before it spreads.\n\nNegative Content Suppression: When negative results appear on the first page of Google, we execute strategic content creation and SEO campaigns to push positive assets — press releases, testimonials, thought leadership articles, and social profiles — above the negative content in search rankings.\n\nReview Generation Strategy: A consistent stream of positive reviews builds trust with potential customers and improves local SEO rankings. We implement ethical review generation systems and encourage satisfied customers to share their experience on the platforms that matter most.\n\nCrisis Management: Data breaches, negative press, viral complaints — our ORM crisis team has response protocols ready to minimize reputational damage and communicate transparently with your stakeholders. Serving Indore, India, and global clients including the USA, UK, UAE, and Australia.\n\nFAQ: Can you remove negative reviews? Fake or policy-violating reviews can be reported for removal; legitimate reviews cannot be deleted but can be outweighed by positive reviews. How quickly can you fix a reputation crisis? Initial suppression efforts begin within 24 hours; full recovery typically takes 3–6 months depending on severity.",
