        name: "Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO)",
        description:
          "Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO) is the science of turning more of your existing website visitors into paying customers — without spending a rupee more on traffic. EDMA's CRO specialists help businesses across India and globally maximize the value of their current traffic through data-driven website optimization that systematically removes barriers to conversion.\n\nOur CRO Process: Comprehensive conversion audit, heatmap and session recording analysis, user behavior research, hypothesis development, A/B and multivariate testing, landing page optimization, funnel analysis, form optimization, and iterative implementation of winning variants.\n\nData-Driven Insights: We use Hotjar, Clarity, Google Analytics 4, and Lucky Orange to understand exactly how users interact with your website — where they click, where they hesitate, and where they abandon. These behavioral insights reveal the specific friction points preventing conversions.\n\nA/B Testing Methodology: Every change we recommend is tested rigorously. We formulate hypotheses based on data, design variants, run statistically significant tests, and implement only the changes proven to increase conversions. No guesswork — only evidence-based optimization.\n\nWhat We Optimize: Landing page headlines and value propositions, call-to-action buttons and placement, form length and field design, page load speed, trust signals (testimonials, certifications, guarantees), checkout flow for ecommerce, and mobile UX.\n\nImpact on ROI: A 1% improvement in conversion rate can double or triple your revenue without increasing ad spend. Our CRO engagements typically deliver 20–150% improvement in conversion rates within 90 days. Serving businesses in Indore, India, and internationally.\n\nFAQ: How long does CRO take to show results? Initial insights emerge within 2–4 weeks; A/B test results typically require 2–8 weeks depending on traffic volume. Do I need high traffic for CRO? A minimum of 1,000 monthly visitors is recommended for statistically valid testing.",
