ong should I retarget website visitors? Most conversion windows fall within 30 days; we recommend 7-, 14-, and 30-day audience windows segmented by recency. What's the minimum traffic needed for retargeting? A minimum of 100 visitors per week on your website enables effective retargeting campaigns.",
